Joaquin’s Middle vs. Name!

Hi! We are naming our little baby boy Joaquin (wah-keen), but we need a middle name! I’m not sure if we should do something a little more traditional, since Joaquin is kind of out there or do something just as unique as Joaquin! What do you think and do you have any suggestions? Please don’t suggest any Hispanic sounding names (Alejandro, Miguel, Xavier, etc.). Although Joaquin is a very Hispanic name, we don’t have announce of Hispanic blood in us. We are both fair skinned with light hair and green/grey eyes. Thanks! -Cale, Sophie, & Joaquin
